    <item>
      <title>Excellent Communicator</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/communicator/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2015 13:38:37 +1000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/communicator/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;portfolio-about-container&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;portfolio-about-item&#34;&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Excellent Communicator&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m a very chill guy to talk to, and I always try to put myself in other people&amp;rsquo;s shoes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I write technical articles aimed at the general audience, which have been very well received on sites such as &lt;a href=&#34;http://gamedev.net&#34;&gt;GameDev.net&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://gamasutra.com&#34;&gt;Gamasutra&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also maintain my own blog at &lt;a href=&#34;http://arianv.com&#34;&gt;arianv.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;portfolio-about-item&#34;&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;blockquote class=&#34;communicator-quote&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
    &amp;ldquo;Super talented and hard working. Also a super friendly guy who is a frequent communicator.&amp;rdquo;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;cite title=&#34;Daniel Stone&#34;&gt;Daniel Stone (Client)&lt;/cite&gt;
  &lt;/blockquote&gt;
  &lt;blockquote class=&#34;communicator-quote&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
    &amp;ldquo;Keep up the good work! I am impressed with how much you have done so far ;)&amp;rdquo;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;cite title=&#34;Sean Diamond&#34;&gt;Sean Diamond (Client)&lt;/cite&gt;
  &lt;/blockquote&gt;
  &lt;blockquote class=&#34;communicator-quote&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
      &amp;ldquo;Thank you for this, we&amp;rsquo;re doing an algorithm course at my university atm and this is exactly what we&amp;rsquo;re learning about, however, I find your examples and explanations much more easy to understand. You&amp;rsquo;re a life saver!&amp;rdquo;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;cite title=&#34;timgranstrom&#34;&gt;Tim Granstrom (Developer)&lt;/cite&gt;
  &lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
